<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate")%>

<div class="row mt-4 mb-5">
    <div class="col-lg-8 offset-lg-2">
        <h1 class="mb-3">About Nestify</h1>
        <p class="lead">
            Nestify helps travelers discover comfortable stays, beautiful homes, and memorable places for every kind of trip.
        </p>
        <p>
            Our goal is simple: make it easy to browse listings, compare locations, and find a stay that feels right. From quiet cabins to city apartments and beachfront homes, Nestify brings different travel experiences into one clean, easy-to-use place.
        </p>
        <p>
            This project is built as a full-stack rental listing app with user accounts, listing management, and a simple browsing experience inspired by modern travel platforms.
        </p>

        <div class="row mt-4">
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                <h5>Comfort</h5>
                <p>Listings are designed to highlight what matters most: photos, price, location, and details.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                <h5>Trust</h5>
                <p>User accounts make the platform ready for personalized and secure features.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                <h5>Discovery</h5>
                <p>Explore stays across cities, beaches, mountains, and unique destinations.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
